<a-row :gutter="gutter">
    <a-col :span="24">
        <a-form layout="inline" class="margin-bottom-lg">
            <a-form-item label="分类">
                <TagGroup :tags="typeTags" @change="bindClickChange"/>
            </a-form-item>
            <a-divider dashed style="margin: 8px 0"/>
            <a-form-item label="时间">
                <TagGroup :tags="dateTags" @change="bindClickChange"/>
            </a-form-item>
            <a-divider dashed style="margin: 8px 0"/>
            <a-form-item label="其他">
                <TagGroup :tags="otherTags" @change="bindClickChange"/>
            </a-form-item>
        </a-form>
    </a-col>

    <a-col :span="24">
        <Tips class="margin-bottom"/>
    </a-col>

    <a-col :span="24">
        <a-list itemLayout="vertical" size="large" class="margin-bottom-lg" :dataSource="notifications">
            <a-list-item slot="renderItem" slot-scope="item">
                <a-list-item-meta :title="item.title">
                    <template slot="description">
                        <a-tag>{{item.type}}</a-tag>
                    </template>
                </a-list-item-meta>
                <Article :sometime="item.dateTime">
                    <template slot="content">{{item.content}}</template>
                </Article>
            </a-list-item>
        </a-list>
    </a-col>
</a-row>
